{"tid":2024441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗國手足係咪唔怕死？","createTime":"2020-05-19T15:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T06:09:06.000Z","uid":92396,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"72d43adc0663131e29fa4447537271561a69b8df","tid":2024441,"uid":92396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:18:43.000Z","msg":"今日收工由元朗行番屋企，沿路竟然見到有文宣！<br />\n行到鄉黑集中地屏山附近既天橋，仲見到天橋上面既膠板同地下都痴左唔同既文宣，而且亦都見到有好多俾人撕走既痕跡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTZRJGN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTZRJGN.png&h=6a12f716&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbTCEff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxbTCEff.png&h=ae03fdcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUG8LVq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUG8LVq.png&h=fadc9358&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVOOLVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVOOLVy.png&h=c4c50034&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwTi780.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwTi780.png&h=8b241467&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Omhcs87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmhcs87.png&h=9626a91b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CCfdW2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCCfdW2z.png&h=544147e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AV2G5V2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAV2G5V2.png&h=12e1c39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然文宣既數量唔多，但仍然覺得呢班手足好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明知呢d圍村有無數咁多鄉黑、藍絲同廢老，隨時都有機會俾佢地衝岀黎打或者係附近暗角位偷影大頭，但依然冒住危險不停痴文宣，盡自己能力去做到最多。<br />\n<br />\n相信呢幾日大家睇到咁多荒謬既事喺香港發生，心情一定好差，仲有好重既無力感，覺得自己好似做乜都冇辦法改變到現況同未來。我自己其實都一樣有呢d感覺，但呢一刻仲未係我地可以放棄既時候！無論你係行咩路線去進行抗爭都好，你喺你既位置都有可以做到既事，就算係痴下文宣、修補連儂牆、Twitter戰線等等都好，都可以岀到一分力。<br />\n<br />\n最後其實想講後日就係721十個月<br />\n8pm 元西見<br />\n<br />\n仲有524 港島見！"},{"pid":"7077555ce7261329ec4becab5d0da379237beb3d","tid":2024441,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"5662cf4ad666cb5702978d5d667b647848d1ad5e","tid":2024441,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家見到文宣真係好稀有"},{"pid":"c4bb1cea05fc2a95177979b893203072091550eb","tid":2024441,"uid":38572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"支持, 不過要超級小心... 可能勁多狗補撚住"},{"pid":"ef718be2f5a96ede74fee83ab8b5097360bacdef","tid":2024441,"uid":92396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"見到岀面又有放負撚岀現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n默默一推"},{"pid":"bdd211ce5eab66400c44029c153b21764c7e7ec5","tid":2024441,"uid":57767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a551c1a0146d0906d506db79e73003dc2bfb1a80","tid":2024441,"uid":130317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"痴線！文宣手足唔該小心d！<br />\n記得唔好自己一個人！<br />\n<br />\nbtw果3隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085b930013bb293ed4f49a86861ff0cb61b38dd4","tid":2024441,"uid":92396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a551c1a0146d0906d506db79e73003dc2bfb1a80","tid":2024441,"uid":130317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T05:56:11.000Z","msg":"痴線！文宣手足唔該小心d！<br />\n記得唔好自己一個人！<br />\n<br />\nbtw果3隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c